Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:26.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}一から心を変えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}(I gotta change, right now)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}Stand up 何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}成り上がり Go break it now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}(Go break it harder!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}一人じゃないって I already know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}だからそう Fight back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}Never gonna stop ブチ壊す 迷いも弱さも
